branchCategory.name: MY2
branchCategory.description: <p>Rodless Cylinder, mechanically jointed series 90-MY2H and 91-MY2H is great for long strokes with compact size and an integrated guide, the MY2 series rodless actuator provides an ideal solution. 90-MY2H is made from materials compatible with secondary battery manufacturing. 91-MY2H includes a "Lub-retainer" and is compatible with low dew point (40°C) applications. Standard strokes are available up to 600mm.</p>
